::Shadow Wing::

She looked at the two bots who had approached her and Lunarpine. 
She looked at the bots hoping to see if they were wearing maximal 
symbols or not.

She glanced at Lunarpine and flashed her small palm dagger to him so 
the other bots couldn't see it.  She wanted him to know that she was 
ready to fight, just in case.
